<h1><a href="../index.shtml">MHS Archives</a>: Memorable Manitobans</h1>
<blockquote>
<table border=0 width="90%"><tr><td>
<table width="100%" border=0 cellpadding="15" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#cbc2cc">
